- **2**: Downgrade to a regular request. If a global consistency read times out, the query is automatically downgraded, and the client does not receive an error.', example='0'),
  polarSccWaitTimeout?: string(name='PolarSccWaitTimeout', description='The timeout period for global consistency.', example='100'),
  readWriteMode?: string(name='ReadWriteMode', description='The read/write mode. Valid values:

- **ReadWrite**: read/write (automatic read/write splitting).

- **ReadOnly** (default): read-only.', example='ReadOnly'),
  resourceOwnerAccount?: string(name='ResourceOwnerAccount'),
  resourceOwnerId?: long(name='ResourceOwnerId'),
  sccMode?: string(name='SccMode', description='Specifies whether to enable global consistency (high-performance mode). Valid values:

- **ON**: Enables the feature.

- **OFF**: Disables the feature.', example='on'),
  VPCId?: string(name='VPCId', example='vpc-2zehr7ghqovftils0****'),
