>
> - If a rule with the specified name does not exist, the system creates a new one based on the provided `RuleConfig`.', example='testrule'),
  ruleNameList?: string(name='RuleNameList', description='A comma-separated list of data masking rule names.

> You must specify either the `RuleName` or `RuleNameList` parameter.', example='testrule'),
  ruleVersion?: string(name='RuleVersion', description='The version of the data masking rule. Valid values:

- v1 (default)

- v2', example='v2'),
